name: Vessels 120: Story Beat 005
description:
14) Tight on Ed and Bill as they turn to each other with huge smiles on their faces
ED: DON’T SOUND LIKE SHE WANTS TO WAIT HER TURN BILL!
15) Tighter still on Ed as his smile turns to an impatient frown.
BETSY (OFFSCREEN): I MEAN IT.
ED: OH YOU DO, DO YOU? WELL THEN CAN I DRAW YOUR ATTENTION TO THE MASSIVE FUCKING GUN I’M HOLDIN’ IN MY HAND!
16) Angle on BETSY, trying to project an air of confidence.
BETSY: I SEE IT. IT’S RARE - REALLY RARE. USES UNIQUE AMMUNITION. EXPENSIVE AMMUNITION. YOU DON’T LOOK LIKE YOU COULD AFFORD IT, AND EVEN IF YOU COULD I’M BETTING YOU WOULDN’T WANT TO WASTE IT ON ME.
